sentences: Joseph Rodney Huffman (born August 4, 1962) is an American musician.

in 2008, he performed live with Lynyrd Skynyrd, filling-in for Billy Powell.
He is currently a member of Hank Williams Jr.'s touring band.
In October 2013, Huffman was diagnosed with a brain tumor.
Not letting surgery set him back he was back on the road with Hank in March of the same year.
